          <p><em>From <a href="https://code.google.com/u/jjbross@gmail.com/">jjbross@gmail.com</a> on May 26, 2012 04:15:19</em></p>

<p>The parameter name has changed to "preferred-language" instead of "language-preference", please refer to <a href="https://code.google.com/p/mapsforge/wiki/GettingStartedMapWriter#Basic_Options">https://code.google.com/p/mapsforge/wiki/GettingStartedMapWriter#Basic_Options</a></p>
